FT  10 JUN 93 / UK Company News: McLeod Russel declines to Pounds 1.9m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
MCLEOD Russel Holdings, the paints producer and distributor which in March
acquired Wheway, the environmental engineering group, announced a reduction
in pre-tax profits from Pounds 2.05m to Pounds 1.91m for the six months to
