Asia, with Samsung Electronics of Korea expected to launch a Dollars 150m
Global Depositary Receipts issue soon.
In the Euro-convertible bond sector, Goldman Sachs launched a Dollars 150m
deal for Home Stake Mining, the North American mining company. The proceeds
will be used to refinance existing bank debt. The seven-year convertible
bonds have a coupon of 5.5 per cent.
