FT  09 JUN 93 / UK Company News: Ingham at Pounds 838,000
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
INGHAM, the worsted spinner and retailer of parts for British classic sports
cars, reported pre-tax profits of Pounds 838,000 for the 15 months to March
31 on turnover of Pounds 11.2m.
