FT  09 JUN 93 / UK Company News: Market falls cut IFG
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Upheavals in currency and interest rate markets contributed to 1992 pre-tax
profits falling by 39 per cent from IPounds 1.09m to IPounds 663,000 (Pounds
